// Autogenerated-style Pigeon output for mtracker (hand-written to match
// `dart run pigeon --input pigeons/messages.dart`, Pigeon ~21.x, Kotlin target).
//
// TODO(native): DO NOT edit by hand long-term. Regenerate with `dart run pigeon`.
// Matches the Dart `messages.g.dart` codec (type ids 129..134) and channel names.

